<div class="title"><h1>SPA Application Template Example</h1></div>
<p>Welcome to the Single Page Application template example.</p>
<p>The purpose of this template is to be used as a guide and as a starting point for the creation of a Single Page Application.</p>
<p>In this example, you will find basic architecture, navigation and structure concepts, as well as some common views or scenarios found in a any web application.</p>
<hr/>
<p>To navigate, between the example pages, you can open the menu in the upper left corner of the toolbar</p>
<p>This template does not cover all the possible scenarios or architectures of an SPA, so it is recommended to use its concepts when they are applicable in the context of each application.</p>